### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "user"
}

### Login user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
